==Example melee setup==
The aim is to maximise damage output while minimising risk. The protected items should be items that either grant very high melee strength bonus increases or a large percentage damage increase like the [[Slayer helmet (i)]]. The [[ultor ring]] and the [[avernic defender]] both give major buffs to the player's offensive stats, and can be used along with cheaper items to deal high damage with limited risk. Items that can be easily replaced such as [[barrows gloves]], [[amulet of strength]], and [[black dragonhide armour|dragonhide armour]] are wise choices as the chance of dying is fairly high. 

If on a [[boss task]], the player can use [[bracelet of slaughter]] to extend the task. This will affect damage output, but lower the player's risk slightly. 

